data.description: Updates just for you! Fresh paint in the formal living room, hallway, and stairway. New flooring in the family room! New flooring and paint in the 1/2 bath. Plenty of space to meet your needs. The sitting room off the master could become a home office or 4th bedroom. Additional finished space in the basement for a rec room or craft room. Fully fenced back yard. Contingent on Seller finding suitable housing. Midland Title West, LLC to handle escrow and closing. See A2A.
